# 🔍 GIRIK Backend — Full System Performance Audit

> [!CAUTION]
> Your DB is on **AWS RDS ap-southeast-2 (Sydney)** and you're likely developing from **India**. Every DB query has **~150-300ms network round-trip latency**. This is the **#1 root cause** of slow APIs. Combined with missing indexes, N+1 queries, bcrypt cost, and S3 signed URL generation on every response — a simple login easily hits 1.5s.

---

## 📊 Bottleneck Summary (Priority Order)

| # | Issue | Severity | Impact | Affected APIs |
|---|-------|----------|--------|---------------|
| 1 | 🌏 **Remote DB (RDS Sydney) from India** | 🔴 CRITICAL | +150-300ms **per query** | ALL APIs |
| 2 | 🔓 **bcrypt.compare with saltRounds=10** | 🔴 CRITICAL | +200-400ms per login | Login, Reset Password |
| 3 | 🔗 **N+1 queries everywhere** | 🔴 CRITICAL | 3-8 extra queries per request | Jobs, Surveys, Certificates, Notifications |
| 4 | 🗄️ **ZERO database indexes** on foreign keys | 🔴 CRITICAL | Full table scans on JOINs/WHERE | ALL APIs with filters |
| 5 | ☁️ **S3 Signed URL on every response** ([resolveEntity](file:///Users/abhinavvishwakarma/work/GIRIK/GIRIK_BACKEND/src/services/fileAccess.service.js#88-126)) | 🟡 HIGH | +100-500ms per response | ALL APIs returning file URLs |
| 6 | 🔐 **Auth middleware does DB query on every request** | 🟡 HIGH | +150-300ms per authenticated API | ALL authenticated APIs |
| 7 | 📢 **Notification service blocking queries** | 🟡 HIGH | 2-5 extra queries per mutation | All status change APIs |
| 8 | 📊 **Dashboard: 9+ parallel queries** | 🟠 MEDIUM | ~1-3s per dashboard load | Admin/GM/TM Dashboard |
| 9 | 🚢 **Vessel list: No pagination for internal roles** | 🟡 HIGH | Loads ALL vessels in memory | GET /vessels |
| 10 | 📝 **API Logger middleware overhead** | 🟠 MEDIUM | Monkey-patches res.send/res.json | ALL APIs |

