### 8. 🚢 Vessel List — No Pagination for Internal Roles

```javascript
// vessel.service.js:74-89
// For other roles, group by company name
const vessels = await Vessel.findAll({   // ALL VESSELS!
    where,
    include: [Client, FlagAdministration],
    order: [['created_at', 'DESC']]
});
```

No `limit`/`offset` for non-CLIENT roles. Fetches ALL vessels, then groups in memory.

