### 9. 📝 API Logger Middleware

```javascript
// api.logger.middleware.js:39-53
res.send = function (data) { ... };   // Monkey-patches res.send
res.json = function (data) { ... };   // Monkey-patches res.json
```

This intercepts every response to log it. While not a huge performance hit, the `console.log` with heavy formatting (emoji, separators) on every request adds overhead, especially with large response bodies.

