## ⏱️ Expected Impact After Fixes

| API | Current | After Fixes | Improvement |
|-----|---------|-------------|-------------|
| Login | ~1.5s | ~400-500ms | **~70% faster** |
| Get Jobs (list) | ~1-2s | ~200-400ms | **~75% faster** |
| Get Job by ID | ~1-2s | ~300-500ms | **~65% faster** |
| Dashboard (Admin) | ~2-4s | ~500-800ms | **~75% faster** |
| Survey Submit | ~2-3s | ~500-700ms | **~70% faster** |
| Any authenticated API | +200-300ms overhead | +5-50ms overhead | **~90% reduction in auth overhead** |

> [!IMPORTANT]
